you are, please. Thank you.

00:10.860 --> 00:14.152
By order of Interpol,
all the art is seized.

00:14.182 --> 00:16.126
You are to stay exactly where you are.

00:16.155 --> 00:20.392
The explosion, somebody did it to us.
Someone very close.

00:20.422 --> 00:21.695
The only way to
get me out of this mess

00:21.725 --> 00:23.457
is to make sure that
Brandeis takes the fall.

00:23.487 --> 00:27.139
Police! Quiet, everyone.
I'm looking for John Brandeis.

00:27.298 --> 00:29.031
You don't snap out of heroin.

00:29.509 --> 00:31.285
Whoever that girl is
that they're looking for.

00:31.315 --> 00:32.613
that's not Elena.

00:32.644 --> 00:34.766
Elena's a code name for a file.

00:35.141 --> 00:37.206
Can't believe
he's out of my life.

00:37.236 --> 00:39.444
